videos.headline: Temple strikes first with short TD
videos.description: Jager Garden squeezes into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown to get Temple on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Temple strikes first with short TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: White fakes handoff, finds Coxie for Memphis TD
videos.description: Brady White fakes the defenders and throws to Damonte Coxie for a 14-yard Memphis touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (White fakes handoff, finds Coxie for Memphis TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Memphis' Gainwell runs in for 25-yard TD
videos.description: Kenneth Gainwell weaves through the Temple defense and gets into the end zone for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Memphis' Gainwell runs in for 25-yard TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Wright hurdles over defender for Owls TD
videos.description: Anthony Russo makes a quick shovel pass to Isaiah Wright who leaps over defenders into the end zone to pick up a 12-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wright hurdles over defender for Owls TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Watkins picks up 23-yard TD run
videos.description: Memphis' Kylan Watkins finds the end zone for a 23-yard Tigers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Watkins picks up 23-yard TD run) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Russo connects with Mack for 12-yard Temple TD
videos.description: Anthony Russo finds Brandon Mack to pad Temple's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Russo connects with Mack for 12-yard Temple TD) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Memphis responds with short TD pass
videos.description: Brady White feeds Tyce Daniel who gets his feet down for a 3-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Memphis responds with short TD pass) 2019/10/12

videos.headline: Memphis' failed lateral leads to 1st loss of season
videos.description: Memphis attempts to run a lateral play to win the game, but it fails and Temple wins 30-28.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Memphis' failed lateral leads to 1st loss of season) 2019/10/12
